import React from "react";

//Material-ui stuff
import Grid from "@material-ui/core/Grid";
import Typography from "@material-ui/core/Typography";

export const RowTasks = () => {

            </Grid>

            <Grid className="borderB" item xs={12}>

            </Grid>
            <Grid className="borderB" item xs={12}>
                <Typography>1</Typography>
            </Grid>
            <Grid className="borderB" item xs={12}>
                <Typography>1</Typography>
            </Grid>
            <Grid className="borderB" item xs={12}>

            </Grid>
            <Grid className="borderB" item xs={12}>
                <Typography>1</Typography>
            </Grid>
            
        </Grid>
    )
}
